title: Pingu - The Complete Series - 10 DVD-Rs - PAL 576i Widescreen
description:
Here I bring up to you Pingu, the Complete Series! It consists on 10 DVDs purchased from a Spanish store in Barcelona, including the DVDs covers and the episodes' titles (in Spanish). The episodes are in 16:9 576i, as they are PAL masters, originally uploaded to RuTracker. 

Enjoy!
